Class PitchSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs3500.music.model.PitchSequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<PitchSequence>

    public class PitchSequence
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<PitchSequence>
    Representation of a sequence of notes at a pitch. A pitch is characterized as a note at an octave.
